Using system dynamics as a strategic tool in businesses, financial or operations fields. Students develop a short resarch project related to their working fields using CLD, Forrester diagramas and performing experiments.

Course periods: 2014-2021

Main contents
==========
* Systems thinking
* Causal loop diagrams
* Stock and flow diagrams
